  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims at increasing the quality and improving of people&apos;s life and reducing the burden to carry water. Communities themselves through focus discussions identified these needs. The project will change the hygiene behaviors of pupils, repair school  wells and toilets, drill new wells, constructs rainwater harvesting and sanitation facilities in new poor districts with high poverty rate. Children are the best entry point for behavior change and carriers of hygiene and health messages</narrative>
